{"tid":451883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞士屠戶公開殺豬　「讓大家知道肉怎麼來」","createTime":"2017-10-29T16:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T11:48:47.000Z","uid":150685,"like":302,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"5fdc509fe80192a2a89bf36947766dd13ac828f8","tid":451883,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171029/640_6fe21902aec25b8a6be47d2f8c282edb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171029%2F640_6fe21902aec25b8a6be47d2f8c282edb.jpg&h=54f5f4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瑞士屠戶本周末在戶外公開殺豬，盼振興歷史傳統。<br />\n德國之音報導，瑞士錫薩赫（Sissach）屠戶在當地時間周日上午於戶外公開殺豬，有150名好奇民眾圍觀，現場也有20多名動保團體抗議。屠夫表示，他們希望強調以人道的屠宰方式進行，也向大眾展示他們口中吃的豬肉是怎麼來的。<br />\n過去瑞士養豬戶會在夏天養胖豬隻，但因為度過冬天豬隻又會變瘦或容易生病，因此在冬天來臨前，屠戶會提前在秋天來臨前大量殺豬，把肉冷凍儲存，內臟或豬血則會被吃掉。<br />\n<br />\n今天上午8時，屠戶們準備電擊槍，將兩頭豬電擊後放血屠宰，之後。有老一輩圍觀民眾表示，過去這樣的景象很常見。<br />\n<br />\n兩名24歲圍觀者表示欣賞這種傳統，「大家可以再一次瞭解豬肉是怎麼來的」。<br />\n但附近的動保團體才高舉標語抗議「動物有感覺，動物正在受苦」，「他們為了你的愉悅承受痛苦」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171029/420_77741425716a2cb7e628dd3c85b608c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171029%2F420_77741425716a2cb7e628dd3c85b608c1.jpg&h=6816031d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171029/420_750986895449bd2be186dbb78afb330f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171029%2F420_750986895449bd2be186dbb78afb330f.jpg&h=537cdc49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171029/1231350/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171029%2F1231350%2F&d=SQ%2BULagOSE9CmQE7HuI2KJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c528fef2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171029/1231350/</a>"},{"pid":"9ec94fda5f9d58701d28c33f13bf60ec80089a68","tid":451883,"uid":54264,"like":667,"dislike":12,"score":655,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"動保團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讓大家知道肉怎麼來呢D係生命教育,日本都有<br />\n呢樣會教細路更珍惜同專重動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f25bf8837a68754d182fcf5346d05625e59583","tid":451883,"uid":29080,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d771e86b658d35d3fa3f7b631bbc3fff509c7e71","tid":451883,"uid":109173,"like":275,"dislike":13,"score":262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:11:44.000Z","msg":"點解唔電埋班環保撚拎去做肥料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"38d2bc5bc0fbf8a13683a2d5fdb394b33d27aab8","tid":451883,"uid":85163,"like":152,"dislike":22,"score":130,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9323a2ea2ae086e617908b5af1d7cd9c6680711e","tid":451883,"uid":46933,"like":173,"dislike":0,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"動物團體抗議做乜<br />\n佢地遊行都係拎d假豬出黎斬話食肉幾殘忍"},{"pid":"7fc82ab489ac6e96c1600ab8d4f16ecc3bef0595","tid":451883,"uid":109173,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔電埋班<span style=\"color: red;\">動</span>保撚拎去做肥料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0612c6134bcf9e529dceb3808daccfc987137e42","tid":451883,"uid":22858,"like":116,"dislike":25,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/a