"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:28:40.000Z","msg":"動物團體係咪無腦 自己唔食肉？"},{"pid":"ede98c7a92a8a49aae4f5250a8c2b8f714d8947b","tid":451883,"uid":30710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動物團體係咪無腦 自己唔食肉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動物撚點會食肉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 動物撚"},{"pid":"3b70884992fd1f94affe9d7cdf38562dbfc33312","tid":451883,"uid":42625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動物團體係咪無腦 自己唔食肉？</blockquote><br />\n佢地真係唔食肉"},{"pid":"abd588d6d666413aa1041b878250331834480a7c","tid":451883,"uid":155289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"有時真係諗唔明動物撚諗咩<br />\n你話折磨動物就話要保護姐<br />\n宜家係人道殺豬有咩問題<br />\n食物鏈本身就係咁 <br />\n老虎食羊隻羊都好痛苦慢慢死唔通你又反對？"},{"pid":"64c505030e748003739aabca6ad3a7ce23f49fa6","tid":451883,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺香港試下叫人唔好食肉，實被人圍攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過有班友走入人地走樓入面高舉反對食魚翅<br />\n俾人屌撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人講緊既係人唔人道既問題，劏豬人地會電暈隻豬先劏<br />\n割鯊魚鰭係生勾勾咁割，你掉返落海佢最後都會死<br />\n五毛又想撈埋一齊講？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你不撚如解釋下食肉既問題點撚樣關五毛事啦撚樣柒頭</span><br />\n魚翅問題唔止係殘唔殘忍，講殘忍香港好多屠場都好殘忍<br />\n更多係因為鯊魚係瀕危動物所以要保育<br />\n<br />\n又反對食翅係一個問題，你直接走入人地私人地方阻住人做生意又係另一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n句子入邊加句五毛會令小學雞覺得自己理據強咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fbece7df32aa235385b711fb51a3577549ae07","tid":451883,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要否定自己食肉本能<br />\n人都係生物 唔見你話大草原d獅子監生食左d動物殘忍？</blockquote><br />\n但佢地有機會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4333a4f7afe3c69d74481ad2410c582f50fd61e","tid":451883,"uid":48834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>動物團體係咪無腦 自己唔食肉？</blockquote><br />\n佢地真係唔食肉</blockquote><br />\n咁佢地其實提倡啲咩?<br />\n全民戒肉?"},{"pid":"ecbf948aa4a27527c52ee464b35b673a1ffa9b2f","tid":451883,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6306aeed75ba45256243c3cd742d6c460ed2e2b","tid":451883,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eed5774c9c56eba4c02b793854a94b51c8db5b2","tid":451883,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要否定自己食肉本能<br />\n人都係生物 唔見你話大草原d獅子監生食左d動物殘忍？</blockquote><br />\n食肉冇問題，問題係食得太多，你睇下美國人飲食習慣就明"},{"pid":"f6a97508ec285dd132d8bff99ee3fee26ec1e2eb","tid":451883,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"講到唔表演你睇平日就唔劏豬咁"},{"pid":"19d5a483c43b234adf34e2d92b949fa1f019136b","tid":451883,"uid":42625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T22:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>動物團體係咪無腦 自己唔食肉？</blockquote><br />\n佢地真係唔食肉</blockquote><br />\n咁佢地其實提倡啲咩?<br />\n全民戒肉?</blockquote><br />\n好多組織都係，想知佢地提倡咩，有個動物解放組織叫PETA可以睇下，啲片好有娛樂性<br />\n好多動物撚都係素食<br />\n香港啲貓狗義工係寵物撚，係唔同嘅嘢"},{"pid":"9b5677f22b6dfbcc46c087c23132e969cb36c7c4","tid":451883,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動保團體應該支持先啱喎，公開呢啲屠宰過程比人知道自己既食物成個過程點黎，分分種多左人選擇go veggie。<br />\n<br />\n我只係諗到一個比較有力既原因反對公開展示屠宰過程，就係附近通勤人士或居民因氣味衛生問題而反對。其實呢個原因反而好正常，因為&quot;not in my backyard&quot; effect。<br />\n<br />\n動保團體short 撚左？佢地又何嘗唔係眼不見為淨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦，就算搬番入屠宰場然後又去人地個場到反？啲左膠真係呢，人地豬肉佬正正經經帶出教育信息，左膠就專走去剝奪人既自由權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常智商就唔會做左膠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8f878a5bd8b80f2321c8f6f9268315ba0330e7","tid":451883,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"我信台狗新聞譯錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c7c3b630fa791d99a222113db2ab6a6bd943a5","tid":451883,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"係台灣新聞同左膠兩者<br />\n我毫不猶豫信左膠"},{"pid":"789ba5c96a87b5934a60101bea795512e3ef518f","tid":451883,"uid":22694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:04:05.000Z","msg":"食肉同食翅差好遠喎<br />\n肉係必需品，有營養<br />\n翅係得個湯好味，唔食又唔會死"},{"pid":"a289bbe95796dcd2a0667959f19276d6ea5e7cb8","tid":451883,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>動物團體係咪無腦 自己唔食肉？</blockquote><br />\n佢地真係唔食肉</blockquote><br />\n咁佢地其實提倡啲咩?<br />\n全民戒肉?</blockquote><br />\n好多組織都係，想知佢地提倡咩，有個動物解放組織叫PETA可以睇下，啲片好有娛樂性<br />\n好多動物撚都係素食<br />\n香港啲貓狗義工係寵物撚，係唔同嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/1080/https://ir0.mobify.com/1080/https://ir0.mobify.com/1080/https://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8GAmFUGMcuA/SaxwEBLNgdI/AAAAAAAABsE/rTAeg0nM5CQ/s400/peta_hitler.jpg\" data-thu